      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior luster, confirms its status as a collector-grade acquisition. Mechanical integrity is absolute, ensuring a driving experience that is as precise as it is exhilarating. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning individual who demands nothing less than perfection.",
