      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely stunning and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have babied this car from day one, and it's in truly pristine shape inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
