    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a masterfully preserved E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a complete double-VANOS overhaul and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity. The six-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise, tactile shifts, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. The suspension geometry is stock and flawless, utilizing fresh OEM bushings to maintain the original handling characteristics. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster",
